The paper deals with the expressive power of families of Boolean circuits and their relationship to logic. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Logic (cs.LO) and Computational Complexity (cs.CC) sub-categories. The paper also studies properties of relational structures such as graphs, which suggests that it could also belong to the Data Structures (cs.DS) and Discrete Mathematics (cs.DM) sub-categories. Finally, the paper discusses the use of circuits in AI, which suggests that it could also belong to the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category.
